description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-The Gleaners / Jean-François Millet

-Cliff of Gréville / Jean-François Millet
-Haystacks: Autumn / Jean-François Millet
-Potato Planters / Jean-François Millet
-Beach in Normandy / Gustave Courbet
-Proudhon and His Children / Gustave Courbet
-The Painter's Studio / Gustave Courbet
-Bonjour Monsieur Courbet / Gustave Courbet
